overview: Showcasing a decade's worth of music videos from legendary punk band Rancid, this electrifying collection features such awesome tracks as "Ruby Soho," "Time Bomb," "Who Would've Thought," "Golden Gate Fields" and "Salvation." Ranging from simple performance pieces to more elaborate productions, each of these videos reaffirms Rancid's reputation as one the most important punk acts of the 1990s.
title: Rancid: The Music Videos: 1993-2003
